org.tiian.flom

Class FlomLockModes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tiian.flom.FlomLockModes

  • public class FlomLockModes
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the constants necessary to map the lock modes used by the C native functions wrapped by the JNI methods. See C header file src/flom_types.h for a verbose description of every lock mode.
